@ECHO OFF
CLS
ECHO Compiling BREAKER.PAS to BREAKER.EXE...
TPC BREAKER /B/UC:\PASCAL > NUL
IF ERRORLEVEL 1 GOTO ERROR
ECHO BREAKER.PAS succesfuly compiled.
ECHO.
ECHO Compressing BREAKER.EXE...
PKLITE BREAKER -E > NUL
ECHO BREAKER.EXE compressed.
GOTO END
:ERROR
ECHO BREAKER.PAS not compiled.
:END
ECHO.